Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=10}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 5,0:00:06.90,0:00:10.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Qual é o seu problema?! Para com essa besteira!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:11.69,0:00:14.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why do you have to fight\Na duel with your friend?! - OG}Por que você precisa lutar?\NVocês dois são amigos!{Z/Ohms/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:14.60,0:00:18.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you give it a little time,\Nyou two will cool down, right?! - OG}Dá um tempo, e vocês dois\Nvão se acalmar, certo?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:18.57,0:00:22.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Usopp too. He just got flared up\Nbecause things were moving quickly. - OG}E o Usopp! Ele só se exaltou\Nporque tudo isso foi muito repentino.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:23.01,0:00:25.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now that we've come this far,\Nwe can't go back. - OG}Já é tarde demais pra voltar atrás.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:26.30,0:00:27.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não é verdade!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:27.57,0:00:31.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You can apologize to him and talk it over again with him! - OG}Você pode pedir desculpas e conversar com ele!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:32.90,0:00:36.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Like I said... it's no longer possible. - OG}Como eu disse... já é tarde demais.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:36.97,0:00:38.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why not? - OG}Como assim?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:38.72,0:00:44.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Usopp isn't stupid enough to risk\Nhis life under the influence of anger. - OG}O Usopp não é burro o suficiente pra\Narriscar a vida por um acesso de raiva.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:44.25,0:00:49.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Besides, if talking it over\Nwould change his opinion, this wouldn't have happened. - OG}Além disso, se bastasse conversar pra mudar\Na opinião dele, não teria chegado a esse ponto.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:51.09,0:00:52.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se você entendeu, me deixa em paz.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:54.44,0:00:55.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:55.60,0:01:00.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm saying, the Franky Family\Ncame here this afternoon, right?! - OG}É isso que eu tô dizendo! A Família Franky\Nveio aqui hoje à tarde, certo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:00.66,0:01:03.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Huh? So what? - OG}Hã? Onde você quer chegar?!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:03.24,0:01:07.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why didn't you beat them all up\Nbeyond recovery then?! - OG}Por que você não aproveitou\Npra acabar com eles de vez?!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:07.33,0:01:11.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you had, Usopp wouldn't have been attacked and felt guilty!}{\q2}Se tivesse feito isso, eles não teriam atacado o Usopp,\Nque agora se sente culpado por tudo!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:01:11.90,0:01:16.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then, instead of going shopping,\Nyou should've stayed and fought them! - OG}Então, em vez de ir fazer compras,\Nvocê devia ter ficado e descido a porrada neles!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:16.84,0:01:19.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I went to get necessary\Nfood as your cook! - OG}É trabalho do cozinheiro conseguir os suprimentos!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:19.25,0:01:21.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop fighting at a time like this! - OG}Não é hora de ficar brigando!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:21.81,0:01:24.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's been enough fighting. - OG}Já teve briga o suficiente.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:01:25.69,0:01:28.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't fight over what's done. - OG}Não briguem pelo que já passou.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:28.00,0:01:31.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami{-san}...! Mas esse idiota é...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:35.09,0:01:39.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Chopper... didn't you... go follow Usopp? - OG}Chopper, você não... foi atrás do Usopp?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:01:42.00,0:01:46.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wanted to continue treating his wounds,\Nbut he turned me away. - OG}Eu queria continuar tratando os ferimentos dele,\Nmas ele me mandou embora.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:47.74,0:01:51.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele arrumou um lugar pra ficar na cidade.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:51.95,0:01:53.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele disse...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:54.33,0:01:59.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He said, "You and I are no longer\Nfriends, so go back to the ship!" - OG}Ele disse: "Você e eu não somos mais\Ncompanheiros, então volta pro navio!"
Dialogue: 5,0:02:04.21,0:02:07.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All that fun time up until\Nthis morning seems like a dream. - OG}Parece que todos os bons momentos\Naté hoje de manhã foram uma ilusão.{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:11.10,0:02:15.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If something is happening\Nto Robin on top of this... - OG}Pra piorar, algo pode ter\Nacontecido com a Robin.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:15.55,0:02:18.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I feel like... the gang... - OG}Eu sinto que... a nossa tripulação...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,está se desmoronando.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:27.11,0:02:29.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São dez horas, a hora marcada.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:29.30,0:02:31.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Usopp is coming. - OG}O Usopp vai aparecer.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:40.65,0:02:43.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You guys, don't leave the ship. - OG}Vocês! Fiquem no navio\Ne não desçam!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:43.76,0:02:45.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entenderam?!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.83,0:02:52.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lá está ele!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:52.57,0:02:54.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:17.70,0:03:20.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So you didn't get cold feet, huh? - OG}Então você não desistiu, hein?{Ohms}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:20.02,0:03:22.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You'd better be sure you're not going to\Nregret this, no matter what happens. - OG}Só não se arrependa depois,\Nindependente do resultado!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:22.93,0:03:25.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is the duel you wanted. - OG}{\i1}Você{\i0} pediu esse duelo!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:25.39,0:03:28.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Of course. You'd better fight seriously. - OG}Claro. Pode vir com tudo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vou virar o jogo.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.73,0:03:34.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu já descobri como te derrotar.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:34.87,0:03:38.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Can't we stop them? Usopp is wounded quite badly! - OG}A gente não pode pará-los?\NO Usopp está muito ferido!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.36,0:03:40.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you can't bear to watch this, go inside. - OG}Entra pra dentro se não aguenta assistir.{Z - CPS}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:41.21,0:03:44.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't lump me in with your past enemies\Nwho didn't know your skills. - OG}Eu não sou como os inimigos que você\Nenfrentou que não conheciam suas habilidades.{Z - CPS}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:44.90,0:03:48.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy. We've known\Neach other for a long time. - OG}Luffy, a gente se conhece faz muito tempo.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.40,0:03:52.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I know about your powers very well. - OG}Eu conheço muito bem os seus poderes.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.13,0:05:47.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't be surprised when\Nyou hear this, Luffy. - OG}O que eu vou dizer pode te surpreender, Luffy...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:47.49,0:05:50.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu tenho 8.000 homens sob meu comando!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.09,0:05:54.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you don't wanna die, surrender now! - OG}Se você preza pela sua vida, se renda agora!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.12,0:05:57.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Oito mil?! Tudo isso?!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.91,0:05:59.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You go inside. - OG}Entra pra dentro logo.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.54,0:06:02.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You don't have any subordinates.\NI know that much! - OG}Eu já sei que você não tem homem nenhum!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:02.59,0:06:05.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Feitiço do Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.13,0:06:08.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You've got razors stuck\Nbetween all your teeth! - OG}Você tem lâminas de barbear\Nentre todos os seus dentes!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.69,0:06:12.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dói só de imaginar isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.00,0:06:13.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entra pra dentro.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.51,0:06:16.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You've got cactus spines inside your fingernails! - OG}Você tem espinhos de cacto\Nenfiados debaixo das unhas!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:18.06,0:06:19.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.52,0:06:21.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Pistol!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.69,0:06:32.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{See?! His body is already... - OG}Tá vendo?! Ele já tá todo arrebentado!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:33.85,0:06:36.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Lethal... Ketchup Star!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.20,0:06:41.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What? Are you sympathizing\Nwith your enemy? What confidence...! - OG}O quê? Sentindo pena\Ndo seu inimigo? Que arrogância!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Flash Dial!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:48.65,0:06:50.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Lethal Egg Star!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.89,0:06:53.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Star!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:53.56,0:06:54.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Star!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.27,0:06:55.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Star!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.98,0:06:59.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que fedor! Estão podres!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:00.05,0:07:03.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Dammit! You jerk! Be serious! - OG}Droga, seu idiota! Leva isso a sério!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.10,0:07:06.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is this silly? I'm very serious, Luffy! - OG}Acha que eu tô brincando?! Eu {\i1}estou{\i0} falando sério, Luffy!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.03,0:07:07.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.03,0:07:09.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is my way of fighting!}É assim... que eu luto!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.69,0:07:12.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, if you open your mouth that big,\Nyou'll have a burn! - OG}Cuidado pra essa boca abertona\Nnão se queimar!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Lethal Tabasco Star!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:18.75,0:07:21.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's hooot! - OG}Tá queimando!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.02,0:07:24.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Watch out when you wriggle! - OG}Cuidado como você se debate!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.67,0:07:28.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Beneath your feet, it's already Caltrop Hell! - OG}Ou seus pés vão conhecer meu Inferno de Estrepes!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.22,0:07:33.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Usopp is in control of the fight! - OG}O Usopp tá controlando a luta!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Escuta, Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.60,0:07:40.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll defeat you without fail\Nand take the Merry... - OG}Pode ter certeza, eu vou te derrotar e ficar com a {\i1}Merry{\i0},
Dialogue: 5,0:07:40.02,0:07:42.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,custe o que custar!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.27,0:07:45.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Lethal Pepper Star!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:47.19,0:07:48.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:56.27,0:07:59.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I told you. I won't use attacks\Nthat won't work on you. - OG}Eu te avisei. Só estou usando\Nataques que funcionam contra {\i1}você{\i0}!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:03.69,0:08:08.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga. Tá fedendo... minha boca tá ardendo...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.84,0:08:10.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e tá doendo!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I won't give you even\Nthe slightest chance to attack! - OG}Você não vai ter chance de revidar!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.50,0:08:14.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{Lethal Shuriken Shooting Stars! - OG}Lethal Shuriken Meteor Shower!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:58.68,0:08:59.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fumaça?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.70,0:09:04.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu estou usando um breath dial.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.41,0:09:09.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You didn't notice the smell\Nbecause of the eggs, did you? - OG}O cheiro foi mascarado pelos ovos.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.78,0:09:16.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The smell of the gas that's filling the area around you! - OG}O cheiro do gás que está enchendo o ar ao seu redor!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.46,0:09:18.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Gás?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.41,0:09:19.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't tell me...! - OG}Ele não...!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.50,0:09:22.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpa! Toma essa!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:22.60,0:09:24.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Fire Star!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What an explosion! - OG}Que explosão!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.71,0:10:03.41,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Usopp, líder dos grandes piratas\Nque reinam sobre esta vila!{SV01 @06:58}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.41,0:10:09.79,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{People praise me—and then praise me more—as "Captain Usopp"! - OG}As pessoas me elogiam — e depois me elogiam\Nmais — e me chamam de Capitão Usopp!{SV01 @07:03}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:18.76,0:10:20.34,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're neat! - OG}{You're a riot!}Você é hilário!{Gord}{SV01 @08:09}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:20.88,0:10:23.34,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, você! Não me insulte!{SV01 @08:12}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:23.34,0:10:24.56,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Por quê?{SV06 @13:22}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.56,0:10:27.27,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é um de nós agora, não é?{SV06 @13:36}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:31.11,0:10:33.74,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Estou vendo uma ilha!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.74,0:10:37.07,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau! Incrível! Que tipo de ilha é essa?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.07,0:10:39.41,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza! Vamos!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.41,0:10:42.50,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Merry{\i1}, a toda velocidade!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.50,0:10:44.95,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,A toda velocidade!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:15.27,0:11:17.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't stand this. - OG}Isso é demais.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.03,0:11:20.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:37.10,0:11:41.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I know... that an attack like that\Nwouldn't take you out. - OG}Eu sabia... que um ataque desses\Nnão ia te derrubar.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I know, Luffy... - OG}Eu te conheço, Luffy.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.30,0:11:47.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{that you fight every battle\Nwith all your strength. - OG}Você se supera em toda luta.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.42,0:11:52.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I know every detail of your skills!}Eu conheço suas habilidades muito bem!{Z}{I can read you like a book! - Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:56.44,0:11:57.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Lethal...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:59.15,0:12:01.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gatling!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.49,0:12:03.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}...Bursting Cactus Star!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:10.41,0:12:12.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.30,0:12:16.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Triple Exploding Stars!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.56,0:12:32.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:32.43,0:12:33.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Pistol!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.99,0:12:48.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.33,0:12:51.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Bazooka!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:56.21,0:12:58.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I have a dial here. - OG}Com esse dial...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.50,0:13:02.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I got... your impact! - OG}Eu absorvi o impacto do seu ataque!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.76,0:13:05.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Impact!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um impact dial!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.07,0:13:22.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Gostou dessa?! Droga!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.79,0:13:58.06,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Usopp, líder dos grandes piratas\Nque reinam sobre esta vila!{SV01 @06:58}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:03.29,0:14:05.65,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Ao nosso novo navio e companheiro!{SV06 @17:23}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.65,0:14:08.66,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,– Saúde!\N– Saúde!{SV06 @17:25}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.01,0:14:12.10,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{I guess that's more like it.}{This is more like it! - OG}Algo assim?{arch - flashback to Gaimon @03:28}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.10,0:14:14.33,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's good!\NLet's draw it on the sail too! - OG}Ficou bom! Vamos desenhar na vela também!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:14.74,0:14:16.21,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{All right! All done! - OG}Beleza! Tudo pronto!{arch: Match Gaimon at 3:44}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.21,0:14:20.54,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now the Going Merry\Npirate ship is all set! - OG}{And now the pirate ship,\Nthe Going Merry, is all set!}Nosso navio pirata,\No {\i0}Going Merry{\i1}, está finalmente pronto!{arch}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:21.70,0:14:25.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Bullet!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.70,0:14:39.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Game over. - OG}A luta acabou.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.61,0:15:25.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You fool...! - OG}Seu idiota...!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.40,0:15:32.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's no way that you\Ncould defeat me, is there?! - OG}Não tinha como...\Nvocê me derrotar!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.86,0:16:01.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't stand this... - OG}Não... chega...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:10.81,0:16:13.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Faça o que quiser com a {\i1}Merry{\i0}.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:17.30,0:16:22.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We'll get a new ship and\Nmove on to the seas ahead! - OG}Quanto a nós, vamos conseguir um navio novo\Ne continuar navegando!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.21,0:16:26.20,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Me deixa sentar aí também, Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.20,0:16:29.17,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Não! Esse é o meu lugar especial!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.17,0:16:31.10,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Ué? O que é aquilo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.67,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você tá fazendo, Usopp?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:32.67,0:16:37.09,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whoa! Hey, you guys!\NNo shoes in Usopp Factory! - OG}Ei! Vocês! Não fiquem andando\Npela Fábrica do Usopp assim!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.80,0:16:50.36,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Um dia, eu vou até Elbaf!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.36,0:16:52.99,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Até a vila dos guerreiros!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.99,0:16:56.99,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{All right, Usopp!\NLet's go there for sure!}Beleza, Usopp!\NVamos com certeza pra lá!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.42,0:17:02.47,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's get this party goin'!\NIt's the night festival before gold-hunting! - OG}Vamos começar a festa!\NÉ o festival da véspera da caça ao ouro!{Gaijin}{Flashback to Skypiea 08 @22:51}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:12.41,0:17:14.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well then, bye, Usopp. - OG}Até mais, Usopp.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:15.16,0:17:18.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Foi divertido.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, não vai, Chopper!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.06,0:17:27.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why not?! - OG}Por que não?!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:27.36,0:17:31.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He was already wounded so badly to start with, and now he got beat up worse! - OG}Os ferimentos dele já eram graves,\Ne agora ele tá em estado pior ainda!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.66,0:17:34.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This isn't a quarrel or a game. - OG}Isso não foi uma briguinha ou um jogo.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:34.41,0:17:39.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So what?! I'm a doctor!\NLet me at least treat him! - OG}E daí?! Eu sou médico!\NMe deixa pelo menos tratar ele!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:43.66,0:17:47.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He lost the duel.\NOn top of that, he gets pitied. - OG}Ele perdeu o duelo.\NA última coisa que ele quer é a nossa pena.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:47.39,0:17:49.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Imagine just how miserable\Nthat must make him feel! - OG}Pensa em como isso faria ele se sentir!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.24,0:17:57.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Imagine how much suffering careless\Nkindness can cause the loser! - OG}Mostrar bondade descuidada pro perdedor\Nsó piora as coisas.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:58.20,0:18:02.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He fought a duel knowing full well this\Nwas how it might turn out! - OG}Ele lutou esse duelo sabendo muito bem\Nque podia acabar assim!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:15.30,0:18:16.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is really tough... - OG}É difícil...!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.30,0:18:20.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's what it means\Nto be a captain, isn't it? - OG}Isso é ser capitão, não é?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:21.40,0:18:23.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't lose yourself. - OG}Não duvide de si mesmo.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:26.01,0:18:31.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you waver, who can we trust? - OG}Se você vacilar, em quem a gente vai confiar?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.19,0:18:45.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's vacate the ship. - OG}Precisamos ir embora.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:55.57,0:19:01.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We can't come back... \Nto this ship, so...... Not ever. - OG}Nós... nunca mais podemos voltar\Npra este navio. Nunca mais.{Z}
